Write a pseudocode to find the maximum of three numbers.
    Start
    input 3 numbers (a, b, c)
    compare, if a > b & a > c, maximum number is a
    Compare, if b > a & b > c, maximum number is b
    compare, if c > a & c > b, maximum number is c
    end

Write a pseudocode to find the average of a list of N numbers.
    Start
    initialize sum = 0
    start loop
        Input a number
        add number to sum
        // continue while N inputs taken
    initialize average = sum / N
    print average
    End